Thought: The AlertEvidence row for IP 202.183.149.174 contains an AdditionalFields JSON blob that may reference the malicious URL or related evidence. I should extract any URLs from the AlertEvidence.RemoteUrl or parse AdditionalFields for an HTTP(s) URL. Query the AlertEvidence record to return RemoteUrl and AdditionalFields fully for inspection.

