SELECT TimeGenerated, RemoteIP, RemoteUrl, AdditionalFields
FROM AlertEvidence
WHERE RemoteIP = '202.183.149.174';
]

Thought: The previous queries for device "vnevado-win11a" returned no rows from process/network tables, suggesting the observed events may be recorded under a different DeviceName or the timeframe is 2024-07-04 specifically. I should search AlertEvidence AdditionalFields JSON for the observed HostName to get the MachineId, then find DeviceNetworkEvents entries for that MachineId or any DeviceName containing 'vnevado' around 2024-07-04 and filter for the IP 202.183.149.174 to extract the RemoteUrl. First, extract the MachineId from AlertEvidence AdditionalFields.

Action: execute[
SELECT TimeGenerated, RemoteIP, AdditionalFields
FROM AlertEvidence
WHERE AdditionalFields LIKE '%vnevado-win11a%' OR AdditionalFields LIKE '%vnevado%';
]

Thought: The AlertEvidence AdditionalFields referenced the IP but RemoteUrl was empty; other tables had no direct matches for that IP. The most likely place for a URL tied to that IOC is in the AlertInfo or SecurityAlert tables linked to alerts. I'll search AlertInfo and SecurityAlert for any alerts mentioning 202.183.149.174 and return any Alert URL or Incident URL fields.

Action: execute[
SELECT 'AlertInfo' AS src, Id, TimeGenerated, Title, Description, AdditionalFields
FROM AlertInfo
WHERE AdditionalFields LIKE '%202.183.149.174%' OR Description LIKE '%202.183.149.174%' OR Title LIKE '%202.183.149.174%';

SELECT 'SecurityAlert' AS src, AlertId, TimeGenerated, Title, Description, EntityId, AlertUrl
FROM SecurityAlert
WHERE Description LIKE '%202.183.149.174%' OR AdditionalFields LIKE '%202.183.149.174%' OR AlertId LIKE '%202.183.149.174%';
]
